title: Nrurita uka ihu na ihu Obama na Romney
sentences: N’agba nke mbụ nrụrịta ụka ahụ, Romney meriri Obama, onye mega anya ụra ụbọchi ha nwere yabụ nrụrịta ụka n’abalị 3 nke ọnwa ọkụtoba a
Ụnyahụ, onye isi ala mba Amerịka, bụ Barack Obama, na Mitt Romney, onye ji aha ndị otu Rịpọlikan azọ ọkwa onye isi ala mba ahụ, nwere nrụrịta ụka
Nke a mere ka o mechera izu ụka abuọ ha abụọ nwere agba nke mbụ nrụrịta ụka ahụ na mahadum Steeti Denver, na Nwenezdee, abalị 3 nke ọnwa ọkụtoba afọ 2012
N’agba nke mbụ nrụrịta ụka ahụ, Romney meriri Obama, onye mega anya ụra ụbọchi ha nwere yabụ nrụrịta ụka n’abalị 3 nke ọnwa ọkụtoba a
N’agba nke abụọ ya ha mere ụnyehụ, Obama jiri anya nwoke ji anyụ nsị pụta
O gosiri Romney na nwata bulie nna ya elu, ọgọdọ nwụchie ya anya
Ndị nta akụkọ na ndị okwu na-adị mma n’ọnụ kwuru na Obama meriri Romney n’agba nke abụọ nrụrịta ụka ahụ
